rence is marginally significant at the ~2 sigma level. The large area of\nour survey makes it possible to study the evolution of the X-ray luminosity\nfunction in the high luminosity range inaccessible with other, smaller area\nROSAT surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 1998 00:27:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
